			x}{b}+\dfrac{x}{c}-1 \right|}{\sqrt{\dfrac{1}{9}+\dfrac{1}{b^2}+\dfrac{1}{c^2}}}
	\end{align*}
	Nhân chéo, bình phương hai vế rồi rút gọn, ta được
	\[ \left(\frac{2}{bc}+\frac{2}{3b}+\frac{2}{3c}\right)x^2-2\left(\frac{1}{3}+\frac{1}{b}+\frac{1}{c}\right)x+1=0. \]
	Chú ý rằng $b+c=3$ nên $\dfrac{1}{b}+\dfrac{1}{c}=\dfrac{3}{bc}$, suy ra
	\begin{align*}
		\frac{4}{bc}x^2-2\left(\frac{1}{3}+\frac{3}{bc}\right)x+1=0 &\Rightarrow x^2-\left(\frac{bc}{6}+\frac{3}{2}\right)x+\frac{bc}{4}=0\\
		&\Rightarrow \left[\begin{aligned}&x=\frac{bc}{6}\\ &x=\frac{3}{2}.\end{aligned}\right.
 	\end{align*}
